('36c6dec8-1184-406e-a630-01666ab0514a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.96,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.25,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced quant researcher who recharges by being around people, not away from them. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. When there is no clean exit abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; when the pressure is off, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.75},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.82}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.96,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A pronounced quant researcher who recharges by being around people, not away from them. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. When there is no clean exit abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; when the pressure is off, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('0a0744bc-1f54-4f9c-85eb-add38ae71332', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.97,"neuroticism":0.39},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.53,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.45,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Event host, pronounced in style: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely; collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. When cornered finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.71},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.77},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.7}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","ipip-neo","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.97,"neuroticism":0.39}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','ipip-neo','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Event host, pronounced in style: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely; collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. When cornered finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('45d0157a-9f9f-4540-aa65-bceb485018a5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.93,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.31,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Newcomer welcomer, pronounced in style: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own; thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. When the stakes rise abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.66},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.6},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.68},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.79}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.93,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Newcomer welcomer, pronounced in style: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own; thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. When the stakes rise abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('280c1662-6043-4856-9ee9-680b93dc14ce', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.41},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.33,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.34,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A steady family peacemaker: absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost, treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and across an ordinary week over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.58},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.41}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A steady family peacemaker: absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost, treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and across an ordinary week over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.', 0.9, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('6019ea6d-03c6-4ada-a8ff-f9ea9f3ae1d5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.94,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.3,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.56,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the downside gets concrete, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. Otherwise, a pronounced the friend who always drives who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and in the unglamorous middle of things texts an apology before confirming anyone is upset.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.79},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.69}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","decision-making","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.94,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','decision-making','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'When the downside gets concrete, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. Otherwise, a pronounced the friend who always drives who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and in the unglamorous middle of things texts an apology before confirming anyone is upset.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('6552e131-7c5c-4fb9-8136-b28cbf2cf22f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.76,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.35,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. A pronounced event host: recharges by being around people, not away from them, would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and without an audience over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.58},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.74},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","outgoing","behavioral","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.76,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','outgoing','behavioral','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. A pronounced event host: recharges by being around people, not away from them, would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and without an audience over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('4590d192-a5b7-4961-ac0a-42068cabc3b8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.79,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.28,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady group-project default leader who absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Recharges by being around people, not away from them. When cornered adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; in the parts nobody grades, remembers who didn''t get invited last time.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.74},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.79,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady group-project default leader who absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Recharges by being around people, not away from them. When cornered adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; in the parts nobody grades, remembers who didn''t get invited last time.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
