('305501d4-af2c-473b-9908-ba8d4186cbdb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.32,"narcissism":0.73,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.31,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Zero-DTE options gambler whose defining move is that they fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Once things get tense, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.82},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.85}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Zero-DTE options gambler whose defining move is that they fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Once things get tense, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('1378ec33-890e-4ee0-90e5-c3c70a7093b5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.93,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.54,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. This onchain copy-trader dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and confuses motion with progress. The instant it becomes irreversible gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it — across an ordinary week, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.78},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.76},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.93,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. This onchain copy-trader dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and confuses motion with progress. The instant it becomes irreversible gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it — across an ordinary week, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('fe5b3701-70db-4fa3-bbb4-24f943a7f1fa', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.91,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.67},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.42,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. This crypto day-trader thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision and treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. When the downside gets concrete finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — once the urgency drains out, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.79},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.72},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.79},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.78}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.91,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.67}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. This crypto day-trader thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision and treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. When the downside gets concrete finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — once the urgency drains out, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('b12b4f4a-7fe9-4616-b166-ad4a65739248', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.56,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.33,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the number turns red, defers to the most senior voice even against their own evidence. Otherwise, a pronounced nonprofit convener who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely and collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and across the quiet stretches over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.56},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.67},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.61},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.68}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","ipip-neo","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','ipip-neo','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'When the number turns red, defers to the most senior voice even against their own evidence. Otherwise, a pronounced nonprofit convener who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely and collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and across the quiet stretches over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('dfd99c2f-4d4c-4a6d-8e74-8d823ca01520', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.88,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.52,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.44,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Reluctant plus-one whose defining move is that they apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Under a deadline, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; laughs first to test whether the room is safe to laugh.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.6}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.88,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Reluctant plus-one whose defining move is that they apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Under a deadline, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; laughs first to test whether the room is safe to laugh.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('b4103820-4d93-4640-89ed-49eded0480a8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.27,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. A pronounced pairs trader: draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone, would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and day to day confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.71},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. A pronounced pairs trader: draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone, would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and day to day confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('7efaba1e-4baf-4446-b3b1-b77c88ca342b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.63},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.62,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.24,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Macro allocator, steady in style: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision; would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. The moment it stops being hypothetical adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.59},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.73},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.63}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Macro allocator, steady in style: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision; would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. The moment it stops being hypothetical adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.', 0.9, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('58b62000-d599-458d-82e2-0a45b4ad2151', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.66},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.49,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced macro allocator who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. The moment it stops being hypothetical adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; when the pressure is off, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.76},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.66}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A pronounced macro allocator who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. The moment it stops being hypothetical adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; when the pressure is off, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('5eca941b-673d-47b0-8bd7-8ce81161a5db', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.34,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. This options seller recharges by being around people, not away from them and apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Once the exit narrows to one door finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — in the small things, exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.76}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. This options seller recharges by being around people, not away from them and apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Once the exit narrows to one door finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — in the small things, exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('eb40edec-8a5c-46cf-891f-6eda19735388', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.71,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.33,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.34,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Quant researcher, steady in style: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision; collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. In a pinch takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.66},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.68},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.71,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Quant researcher, steady in style: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision; collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. In a pinch takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('5fc018cf-27ff-4a7a-b696-4c54657429bd', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.86,"neuroticism":0.4},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.33,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.53,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. A pronounced group-project default leader: would rather lose a point than win an argument badly, reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and as a rule mediates conflicts they secretly started.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.86,"neuroticism":0.4}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. A pronounced group-project default leader: would rather lose a point than win an argument badly, reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and as a rule mediates conflicts they secretly started.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('6862f05e-6b63-4a15-b2d8-ea0d4b10eea5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.62,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.37,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady pairs trader who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. The moment risk appears takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; in the pattern nobody else tracks, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.68},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","open-minded","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','open-minded','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady pairs trader who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. The moment risk appears takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; in the pattern nobody else tracks, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.9, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('83f51aa8-4b0f-481b-a02e-26f765c46f48', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.67,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.43,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Once things get tense, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. Otherwise, a steady delta-neutral market maker who fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and in the pattern nobody else tracks names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Once things get tense, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. Otherwise, a steady delta-neutral market maker who fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and in the pattern nobody else tracks names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.91, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('5b00f99c-006c-42ab-82a4-9526013a5adf', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.62,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.36,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. A steady DeFi yield farmer: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision, reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and without an audience averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.79},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. A steady DeFi yield farmer: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision, reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and without an audience averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('45034af5-b503-45cf-b26d-93297e1fa583', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.47},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.26,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Wedding-party diplomat, pronounced in style: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own; recharges by being around people, not away from them. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. The moment it stops being hypothetical abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.57},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.62}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","behavioral","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.47}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','behavioral','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Wedding-party diplomat, pronounced in style: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own; recharges by being around people, not away from them. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. The moment it stops being hypothetical abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('f0044eb1-4d64-45b9-8fdc-430bc18304ce', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.65,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.46,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.23,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Neighborhood connector whose defining move is that they treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. The moment risk appears, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; keeps a mental ledger of social debts.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.58},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","outgoing","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.65,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','outgoing','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Neighborhood connector whose defining move is that they treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. The moment risk appears, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; keeps a mental ledger of social debts.', 0.93, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('5ffcaeff-aae1-4fc0-8fc7-539fb808e3fc', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.85,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.32,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Under pressure, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. Otherwise, a pronounced social-media strategist who absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and in the routine of it can sense a mood shift from the doorway.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.67},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.6}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","cognition","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.85,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','cognition','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Under pressure, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. Otherwise, a pronounced social-media strategist who absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and in the routine of it can sense a mood shift from the doorway.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('b7de13b6-ba4c-46e5-ab6b-d974a7e50eb4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.69,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.46,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.36,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. A steady event host: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely, would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and day to day over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.57},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.58},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.63},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.66}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.69,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. A steady event host: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely, would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and day to day over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.', 0.91, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('7a641de9-3d4d-4446-8fa1-43f4810d9eac', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.42,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady index-fund holdout who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Once things get tense abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; in the parts nobody grades, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.71},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady index-fund holdout who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Once things get tense abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; in the parts nobody grades, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('5852cd1b-4910-4d20-b126-4ca890cf7a3d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.89,"neuroticism":0.42},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.45,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The friend who always drives, pronounced in style: absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost; dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.74},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.77},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.6}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.89,"neuroticism":0.42}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'The friend who always drives, pronounced in style: absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost; dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('7107e925-0820-4737-9c6c-90258b51a01b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.87,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.25},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.4,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Peer mentor, pronounced in style: absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost; over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. When the number turns red finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.63},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.72},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.6}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","behavioral","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.87,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','behavioral','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Peer mentor, pronounced in style: absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost; over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. When the number turns red finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('48389a4e-0e4d-4565-920d-d04da320a0d7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.43,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. This zero-DTE options gambler thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision and reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. The instant the deadline moves up abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way — in the parts nobody grades, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.73},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.76}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. This zero-DTE options gambler thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision and reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. The instant the deadline moves up abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way — in the parts nobody grades, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('09767408-f598-4ac4-9ed3-f83082f23b95', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.62},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.33,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.52,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Dividend-yield chaser whose defining move is that they thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. When the number turns red, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.7},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.62}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Dividend-yield chaser whose defining move is that they thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. When the number turns red, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.92, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('ad850a11-6d9b-4ed1-abbe-4ba57ca85d48', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.8,"neuroticism":0.41},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.56,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.26,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. This reluctant plus-one absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. When someone is watching the outcome finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view — left to their own devices, over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.6},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.65},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.64}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.8,"neuroticism":0.41}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. This reluctant plus-one absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. When someone is watching the outcome finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view — left to their own devices, over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.', 0.92, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('3f6861bc-e502-419f-9317-a2504e46a917', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.65},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.37,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Once the exit narrows to one door, is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest. Otherwise, a pronounced delta-neutral market maker who recharges by being around people, not away from them and spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and when the stakes are trivial apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.71},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.65}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Once the exit narrows to one door, is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest. Otherwise, a pronounced delta-neutral market maker who recharges by being around people, not away from them and spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and when the stakes are trivial apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
