('63e5cadd-cc1a-4163-bc6d-b5a8779f9133', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.85,"neuroticism":0.41},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.31,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced group-project default leader who takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; in the version no one reviews, laughs first to test whether the room is safe to laugh.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.75},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.58}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.85,"neuroticism":0.41}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A pronounced group-project default leader who takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; in the version no one reviews, laughs first to test whether the room is safe to laugh.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('feca811a-38ed-49d7-aab6-ae866bd82aec', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.82,"neuroticism":0.42},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.31,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.27,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the number turns red, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. Otherwise, a pronounced retail momentum chaser who narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it and reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and across the quiet stretches treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.78},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.82,"neuroticism":0.42}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'When the number turns red, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. Otherwise, a pronounced retail momentum chaser who narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it and reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and across the quiet stretches treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('8a03fe2d-ba6d-4dbc-9035-b2f85bac5c71', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.39,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When there is no clean exit, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a steady macro allocator who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and in the routine of it refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.57},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.58},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.72},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.54}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","open-minded","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','open-minded','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'When there is no clean exit, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a steady macro allocator who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and in the routine of it refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.92, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('b6573daf-e0e2-401e-a7e4-b7d04c614a45', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.62,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.46,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady unofficial group historian who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Once things get tense takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; in the version no one reviews, reads the room then performs to it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.76}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","outgoing","behavioral","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','outgoing','behavioral','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady unofficial group historian who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Once things get tense takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; in the version no one reviews, reads the room then performs to it.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('00bae68e-88b1-47a9-83ca-ebf328e2f627', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.69,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.87,"neuroticism":0.38},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.25,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The instant it becomes irreversible, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. Otherwise, a pronounced the one who remembers everyone''s order who takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own and checks its own anxiety like a data point instead of obeying it. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and when the stakes are trivial remembers everyone birthday and no one boundaries.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.6},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.76}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","ipip-neo","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.69,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.87,"neuroticism":0.38}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','ipip-neo','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'The instant it becomes irreversible, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. Otherwise, a pronounced the one who remembers everyone''s order who takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own and checks its own anxiety like a data point instead of obeying it. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and when the stakes are trivial remembers everyone birthday and no one boundaries.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('9dcfcd36-2413-48bc-b2dd-d39993759b71', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.68,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.92,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.62,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.37,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Wedding-party diplomat, pronounced in style: reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it; would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. When the stakes rise gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.7},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.76}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","decision-making","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.68,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.92,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','decision-making','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Wedding-party diplomat, pronounced in style: reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it; would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. When the stakes rise gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('1f7c4a2c-2126-4d8a-b14b-68aa57000f28', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.81,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.49,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Value investor whose defining move is that they draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. When the downside gets concrete, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.6},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.59},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.81,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Value investor whose defining move is that they draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. When the downside gets concrete, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.93, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('10cfd0d4-b955-4993-bc93-a132878eed38', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.92,"neuroticism":0.41},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.33,"narcissism":0.52,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.39,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Event host, pronounced in style: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely; collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. When the downside gets concrete finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.73},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.71},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.72}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.92,"neuroticism":0.41}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Event host, pronounced in style: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely; collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. When the downside gets concrete finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('c634c8ca-5bb0-409e-a5c9-f5e06f216548', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.33,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Penny-stock gambler, pronounced in style: draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone; would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Once the exit narrows to one door finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.72},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Penny-stock gambler, pronounced in style: draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone; would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Once the exit narrows to one door finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('e45696bb-3721-49c4-9666-9a7710f4ceed', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.86,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.45,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced nonprofit convener who measures decisions by who they might upset. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; once the urgency drains out, remembers everyone birthday and no one boundaries.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.76},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.65}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.86,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A pronounced nonprofit convener who measures decisions by who they might upset. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; once the urgency drains out, remembers everyone birthday and no one boundaries.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('91e21964-7cd1-4264-8a89-20f29bdef050', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.38,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. This options seller fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has — in the unglamorous middle of things, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. This options seller fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has — in the unglamorous middle of things, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('f7517610-fa56-4a4b-bd9f-142e2c4e40a3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.29,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Retail momentum chaser whose defining move is that they fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. When someone is watching the outcome, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery; screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.72},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.69},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Retail momentum chaser whose defining move is that they fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. When someone is watching the outcome, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery; screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('a918285d-6601-4e1d-8db4-0974ea940343', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.67},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.52,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A steady macro allocator: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades, would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and left to their own devices calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.62},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","open-minded","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.67}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','open-minded','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A steady macro allocator: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades, would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and left to their own devices calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.92, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('207485e0-1d34-487e-8476-f6db94dba82d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.54,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Prop-desk scalper whose defining move is that they narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Once things get tense, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.81},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.78},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Prop-desk scalper whose defining move is that they narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Once things get tense, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('eef379f7-2871-4a8c-a25a-1e04548a41b5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.86,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.32,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced reluctant plus-one who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Under a deadline takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; in the unglamorous middle of things, mediates conflicts they secretly started.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.59},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.69},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.71},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.64}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.86,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A pronounced reluctant plus-one who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Under a deadline takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; in the unglamorous middle of things, mediates conflicts they secretly started.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('1274fa2b-a08c-4307-a2cf-5c40a1df98a6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.86,"neuroticism":0.47},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.36,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Event host, pronounced in style: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own; fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. The moment risk appears finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.72},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.76}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.86,"neuroticism":0.47}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Event host, pronounced in style: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own; fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. The moment risk appears finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view.', 0.95, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('75fc0c06-173f-41a5-a502-7034ca616924', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.83,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.42,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Perps degen whose defining move is that they treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. The moment risk appears, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.8},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.83,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Perps degen whose defining move is that they treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. The moment risk appears, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('eda97503-9d7e-4c60-af9d-379ed190f744', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.62,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.42,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. This retail momentum chaser narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it and measures decisions by who they might upset. Under pressure gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it — in the parts nobody grades, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.54},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.72},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. This retail momentum chaser narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it and measures decisions by who they might upset. Under pressure gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it — in the parts nobody grades, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('90b8d8ef-bc79-4b3a-a0c8-0e25372bbc46', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.91,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.54,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A pronounced online moderator: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own, treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and once the urgency drains out keeps score of favors without meaning to.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.64},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.76},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.91,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A pronounced online moderator: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own, treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and once the urgency drains out keeps score of favors without meaning to.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('51edbfde-a441-4849-8745-45ebebe042ac', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.7},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.69,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.39,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. A pronounced penny-stock gambler: recharges by being around people, not away from them, takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and in the pattern nobody else tracks checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.77},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.76}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.7}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. A pronounced penny-stock gambler: recharges by being around people, not away from them, takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and in the pattern nobody else tracks checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('70d05f6e-7f6f-4f19-9ce0-4a38bb2ab296', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.88,"neuroticism":0.45},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.56,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Unofficial group historian, pronounced in style: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own; cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. The instant the deadline moves up finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.7},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.59},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.75}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","risk","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.88,"neuroticism":0.45}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','risk','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Unofficial group historian, pronounced in style: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own; cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. The instant the deadline moves up finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
