('fa1a2954-2a0d-4fa4-8926-3ef0ee99c539', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.38,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced futures spreader who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. The instant it becomes irreversible adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; in the routine of it, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.78},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A pronounced futures spreader who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. The instant it becomes irreversible adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; in the routine of it, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('b8d0cea5-aa55-4ee5-ab38-3498fe4902ae', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.82,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.38,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady social-media strategist who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. In a pinch gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; in the small things, texts an apology before confirming anyone is upset.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.74},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.82,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady social-media strategist who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. In a pinch gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; in the small things, texts an apology before confirming anyone is upset.', 0.93, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('e3555c4a-8e97-44e1-9614-febf313fc835', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.91,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.62,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.45,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. A pronounced event host: reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it, thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and in the small things can sense a mood shift from the doorway.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.72},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.68}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.91,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. A pronounced event host: reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it, thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and in the small things can sense a mood shift from the doorway.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('5eaab1c8-54b5-42be-998d-e91586351014', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.3,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The instant it becomes irreversible, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. Otherwise, a pronounced discretionary swing trader who fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to and reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and once the urgency drains out rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.78},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.8}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'The instant it becomes irreversible, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. Otherwise, a pronounced discretionary swing trader who fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to and reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and once the urgency drains out rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('e9659a1b-674c-4552-a2b8-39b8f8f22ea1', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.97,"neuroticism":0.39},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.31,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced social-media strategist who reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Recharges by being around people, not away from them. When there is no clean exit adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; in the unglamorous middle of things, says yes out loud and no internally.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.82},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.71}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.97,"neuroticism":0.39}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A pronounced social-media strategist who reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Recharges by being around people, not away from them. When there is no clean exit adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; in the unglamorous middle of things, says yes out loud and no internally.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('a90a6d2a-d2b4-45a5-8b49-446b2a53a167', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.66,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.53,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady newcomer welcomer who absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; as a rule, over-commits to plans they later dread.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.63},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.72}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.66,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady newcomer welcomer who absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; as a rule, over-commits to plans they later dread.', 0.86, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('c906d63d-546c-4a45-be08-70eb75da87fc', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.8,"neuroticism":0.62},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.32,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.52,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. When the stakes rise, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.69},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.83}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.8,"neuroticism":0.62}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. When the stakes rise, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('d8461227-9bb0-4fb9-970d-3261ada9cd21', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.27,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. This prop-desk scalper narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it and hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. When the walls close in treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss — in the routine of it, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.56},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.57},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. This prop-desk scalper narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it and hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. When the walls close in treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss — in the routine of it, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('8b80e8fd-2fec-4c77-aa7f-baef11e35675', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.92,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.35,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Once things get tense, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. Otherwise, a pronounced onchain copy-trader who recharges by being around people, not away from them and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and day to day backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.81},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.75},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.92,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Once things get tense, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. Otherwise, a pronounced onchain copy-trader who recharges by being around people, not away from them and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and day to day backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('5cf930bf-4c4e-4882-a47f-2658a9fdd1a1', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.56,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady event host who recharges by being around people, not away from them. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. When the number turns red adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; on a slow afternoon, laughs first to test whether the room is safe to laugh.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.6},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.74}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","outgoing","behavioral","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','outgoing','behavioral','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady event host who recharges by being around people, not away from them. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. When the number turns red adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; on a slow afternoon, laughs first to test whether the room is safe to laugh.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('b5e52961-9204-4620-a69f-79903abcb387', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.93,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.42,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Delta-neutral market maker whose defining move is that they dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. When the walls close in, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.83},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.64},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.93,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Delta-neutral market maker whose defining move is that they dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. When the walls close in, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('0c67bfd1-2ea9-47e9-a809-6a5ba7008c90', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.3,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Quant researcher, steady in style: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision; collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Under a deadline gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Quant researcher, steady in style: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision; collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Under a deadline gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it.', 0.88, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('c9b56197-3aec-4dd2-8242-c8aeb8dcd204', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.44,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Community manager whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Once things get tense, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; remembers who didn''t get invited last time.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.72},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.64},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","open-minded","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','open-minded','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Community manager whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Once things get tense, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; remembers who didn''t get invited last time.', 0.93, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('95cc6e97-0aa4-41d9-8a9e-d87f531f2b6b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.92,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.81,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.49,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The moment risk appears, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a pronounced DeFi yield farmer who recharges by being around people, not away from them and reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and when no one is watching calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.92,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'The moment risk appears, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a pronounced DeFi yield farmer who recharges by being around people, not away from them and reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and when no one is watching calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('45de8896-2648-4a57-a914-cb2df8e7b9bd', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.95,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.31,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Longtime regular at the same three places whose defining move is that they takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Under pressure, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; says yes out loud and no internally.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.63},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.8}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.95,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Longtime regular at the same three places whose defining move is that they takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Under pressure, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; says yes out loud and no internally.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('b0b34695-d506-4f3e-9839-65ff1609197b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.85,"neuroticism":0.35},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.62,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.38,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. A pronounced the one who remembers everyone''s order: absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost, draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and when the stakes are trivial keeps a mental ledger of social debts.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.66},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.68},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.72}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.85,"neuroticism":0.35}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. A pronounced the one who remembers everyone''s order: absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost, draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and when the stakes are trivial keeps a mental ledger of social debts.', 0.93, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('d77c0257-f985-43f7-8ddc-d32e8ddd7081', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.88,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.3,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Group-chat ringleader whose defining move is that they measures decisions by who they might upset. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Once the exit narrows to one door, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; remembers everyone birthday and no one boundaries.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.66},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.76},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.63},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","behavioral","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.88,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','behavioral','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Group-chat ringleader whose defining move is that they measures decisions by who they might upset. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Once the exit narrows to one door, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; remembers everyone birthday and no one boundaries.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('a9be8c7e-cb45-4042-a90f-cc02ad72d260', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.88,"neuroticism":0.37},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.55,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. This unofficial group historian apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault and recharges by being around people, not away from them. The instant the deadline moves up gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it — across the quiet stretches, says yes out loud and no internally.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.66},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.81}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.88,"neuroticism":0.37}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. This unofficial group historian apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault and recharges by being around people, not away from them. The instant the deadline moves up gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it — across the quiet stretches, says yes out loud and no internally.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('e3910e9e-d86e-4f06-a54a-8d361ddb033c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.95,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.47},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.35,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Once the exit narrows to one door, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. Otherwise, a pronounced futures spreader who recharges by being around people, not away from them and absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and in the routine of it names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.63},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.77},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.79},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.95,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.47}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Once the exit narrows to one door, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. Otherwise, a pronounced futures spreader who recharges by being around people, not away from them and absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and in the routine of it names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63