('8d9243f4-beb9-43b6-8e6b-8d73eea6c3ef', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.69,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.49,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. This commodities speculator reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. When cornered finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — when the stakes are trivial, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.71},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","open-minded","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','open-minded','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. This commodities speculator reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. When cornered finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — when the stakes are trivial, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('d4514566-6fae-43ac-bd9d-b42a1ed1d903', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.81,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.33,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.35,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. This options seller measures decisions by who they might upset and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Under a deadline abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way — when the stakes are trivial, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.66},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","accommodating","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.81,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','accommodating','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. This options seller measures decisions by who they might upset and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Under a deadline abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way — when the stakes are trivial, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.95, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('54a455ce-2723-4867-bdc0-5b4686187544', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.86,"neuroticism":0.47},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.62,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.38,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Family peacemaker whose defining move is that they takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. When the downside gets concrete, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; reads the room then performs to it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.59},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.8},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.59}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.86,"neuroticism":0.47}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Family peacemaker whose defining move is that they takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. When the downside gets concrete, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; reads the room then performs to it.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('0cf00079-cd4d-4b1c-a7c0-a7617ea612cf', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.46,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Algorithmic market-maker, pronounced in style: narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it; confuses motion with progress. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Under pressure cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.65},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.76}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Algorithmic market-maker, pronounced in style: narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it; confuses motion with progress. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Under pressure cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('fcf0c414-1643-4aa7-89e8-36423a664b0e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.93,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.44,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Unofficial group historian, pronounced in style: measures decisions by who they might upset; draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. The instant it becomes irreversible takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.64},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.73},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.61}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","risk","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.93,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','risk','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Unofficial group historian, pronounced in style: measures decisions by who they might upset; draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. The instant it becomes irreversible takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('b4c1c90b-41bf-46ca-b50d-dc90b4375c18', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.67,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.38,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. This onchain copy-trader draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone and would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. The moment it stops being hypothetical finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — when the pressure is off, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.59},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.77}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. This onchain copy-trader draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone and would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. The moment it stops being hypothetical finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — when the pressure is off, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('90a2c818-6a70-4c75-94f9-00880429a3a7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.41,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady airdrop farmer who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. When cornered adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; in the parts nobody grades, apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.73},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","open-minded","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','open-minded','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady airdrop farmer who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. When cornered adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; in the parts nobody grades, apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
