('3dd9f059-8f39-4bc1-99c8-f56cc4b7e390', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.79,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.42,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the number turns red, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a steady nonprofit convener who narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it and defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and when no one is watching says yes out loud and no internally.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.68},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.63}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.79,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'When the number turns red, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a steady nonprofit convener who narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it and defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and when no one is watching says yes out loud and no internally.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('eb7f1307-2b1b-496b-84de-5139c23bd9db', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.68,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.46,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. A steady event host: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely, reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and without an audience texts an apology before confirming anyone is upset.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.6},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.56},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.57}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.68,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. A steady event host: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely, reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and without an audience texts an apology before confirming anyone is upset.', 0.95, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('4f61223f-2320-49e6-a9ef-197421355302', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.8,"neuroticism":0.41},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.37,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Neighborhood connector whose defining move is that they absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.54},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","ipip-neo","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.8,"neuroticism":0.41}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','ipip-neo','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Neighborhood connector whose defining move is that they absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.', 0.95, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('97f66464-b20b-4631-a8ca-87f669029e38', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.95,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.33,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.43,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Airdrop farmer whose defining move is that they recharges by being around people, not away from them. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. The instant it becomes irreversible, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.76},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.68},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.77}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.95,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Airdrop farmer whose defining move is that they recharges by being around people, not away from them. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. The instant it becomes irreversible, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('3a5583c8-54ab-4fe3-b3dd-8b434053e664', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.9,"neuroticism":0.41},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.33,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Community manager whose defining move is that they measures decisions by who they might upset. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Once the exit narrows to one door, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; defuses tension with a joke that lands most of the time.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.6},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.71},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.8}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","risk","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.9,"neuroticism":0.41}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','risk','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Community manager whose defining move is that they measures decisions by who they might upset. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Once the exit narrows to one door, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; defuses tension with a joke that lands most of the time.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('53f5d0c7-a3ac-4667-a91d-b10334bc22e9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.87,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.25},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.41,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. This unofficial group historian absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost and over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. When the stakes rise takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis — in the routine of it, keeps a mental ledger of social debts.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.59},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.65},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","cognition","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.87,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','cognition','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. This unofficial group historian absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost and over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. When the stakes rise takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis — in the routine of it, keeps a mental ledger of social debts.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('f52f49da-97e8-4fbb-b6b2-31e9501bca99', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.73,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.3,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced macro allocator who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. When the number turns red abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; in the pattern nobody else tracks, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.72},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.72},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A pronounced macro allocator who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. When the number turns red abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; in the pattern nobody else tracks, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('104d48fd-fca0-47a6-8b26-058e2fdf32c2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.71,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.92,"neuroticism":0.36},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.54,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.45,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. A pronounced group-project default leader: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely, treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and across an ordinary week over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.63},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.64},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.77},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.68}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.71,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.92,"neuroticism":0.36}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. A pronounced group-project default leader: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely, treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and across an ordinary week over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('6dac4a54-8412-4930-80d7-42fd430e6e56', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.33,"narcissism":0.67,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.26,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady onchain copy-trader who treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. When someone is watching the outcome adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; when the pressure is off, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.6},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady onchain copy-trader who treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. When someone is watching the outcome adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; when the pressure is off, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.9, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('f17a7675-fff1-4b93-b3c2-8a5edc734e5b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.9,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.28,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. This peer mentor would rather lose a point than win an argument badly and plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. The moment risk appears finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — when the pressure is off, remembers everyone birthday and no one boundaries.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.75},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.6},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.76}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.9,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. This peer mentor would rather lose a point than win an argument badly and plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. The moment risk appears finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — when the pressure is off, remembers everyone birthday and no one boundaries.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('a900eb55-b96d-4554-a00a-5b9ccc4e1b3e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.36,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Crypto day-trader, steady in style: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to; apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Once things get tense abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.67},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Crypto day-trader, steady in style: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to; apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Once things get tense abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('3d68cf24-a48d-431a-9868-2581e8b0025b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.88,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.52,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.23,"alpha":0.95,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced social-media strategist who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. When the safe option quietly expires finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; day to day, over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.58},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.63},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.66}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.88,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A pronounced social-media strategist who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. When the safe option quietly expires finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; day to day, over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('07cf0b5f-da41-42d0-8756-dffe312d430b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.91,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.77,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.57,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced crypto day-trader who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. In a pinch abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; when the pressure is off, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.66},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.83},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.63},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.82}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.91,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A pronounced crypto day-trader who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. In a pinch abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; when the pressure is off, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('44967058-aee9-40c3-8da0-f4b19b941ce4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.93,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.26,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When cornered, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. Otherwise, a pronounced event host who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and in the routine of it mediates conflicts they secretly started.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.89},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.83},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.7}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","risk","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.93,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','risk','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'When cornered, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. Otherwise, a pronounced event host who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and in the routine of it mediates conflicts they secretly started.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('d1645ae2-e42a-4d48-9a3b-d7348d35b8f3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.31,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A pronounced retail momentum chaser: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision, chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and when no one is watching exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.78}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A pronounced retail momentum chaser: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision, chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and when no one is watching exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('84f49fc4-12da-4c7d-8515-aae2a8c2169a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.83,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.4,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Newcomer welcomer, steady in style: reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it; gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. In a pinch gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.73},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.65},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.6},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","cognition","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.83,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','cognition','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Newcomer welcomer, steady in style: reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it; gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. In a pinch gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it.', 0.95, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('298431f3-e313-484f-bc88-2ca4cfb8eb6b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.52,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A steady perps degen: dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet, improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and in the parts nobody grades exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.65},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.77},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A steady perps degen: dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet, improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and in the parts nobody grades exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.93, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('8b2524d6-4e23-48f5-94c7-ab570da590d9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.37,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Discretionary swing trader whose defining move is that they treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. When there is no clean exit, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.54},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.56},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Discretionary swing trader whose defining move is that they treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. When there is no clean exit, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('67cc9826-d92b-450e-beee-2d4370388aa4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.44,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Onchain copy-trader, steady in style: narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it; absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. When cornered gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.78},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.6},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Onchain copy-trader, steady in style: narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it; absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. When cornered gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it.', 0.91, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('c51329d1-a260-4edf-86a8-ff7b4063cd2e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.36,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced value investor who fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Measures decisions by who they might upset. When the safe option quietly expires adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; across the quiet stretches, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.76},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A pronounced value investor who fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Measures decisions by who they might upset. When the safe option quietly expires adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; across the quiet stretches, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('c4e3331d-54cd-4270-bff3-6456cf0c3f85', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.93,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.34,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Under a deadline takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; left to their own devices, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.56},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.77},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.79},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.93,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Under a deadline takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; left to their own devices, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('dd41de45-de04-4ee0-94bf-fd8804a4b950', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.55,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. This airdrop farmer recharges by being around people, not away from them and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. The instant the deadline moves up takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis — without an audience, apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. This airdrop farmer recharges by being around people, not away from them and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. The instant the deadline moves up takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis — without an audience, apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.95, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('34ac7330-f8c7-439e-9c34-4bdf9eb4ba52', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.66,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.82,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.5,"alpha":0.95,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. This online moderator measures decisions by who they might upset and treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. The moment it stops being hypothetical finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — without an audience, mediates conflicts they secretly started.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.58},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.66},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","behavioral","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.66,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.82,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','behavioral','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. This online moderator measures decisions by who they might upset and treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. The moment it stops being hypothetical finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — without an audience, mediates conflicts they secretly started.', 0.92, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('0692cd52-68a9-4df2-b3cc-94bbcd183cf7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.56,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.26,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The moment risk appears, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. Otherwise, a steady group-project default leader who takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and as a rule reads the room then performs to it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.56},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.66},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.52}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","risk","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','risk','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'The moment risk appears, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. Otherwise, a steady group-project default leader who takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and as a rule reads the room then performs to it.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('10941ce9-c635-4149-9eee-c5f6f723b382', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.68},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.29,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A pronounced futures spreader: narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it, reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and as a rule averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.59},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.77},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.68},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.68}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A pronounced futures spreader: narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it, reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and as a rule averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('cbf6ae54-bd4e-4e58-a33b-9d42e0350637', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.97,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.83,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.24,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Once the exit narrows to one door, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. Otherwise, a pronounced liquidation-bot operator who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and across the quiet stretches averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.74},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.87},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.65},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.8}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.97,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Once the exit narrows to one door, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. Otherwise, a pronounced liquidation-bot operator who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and across the quiet stretches averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('3f6dbb72-8660-4cd7-9c92-96f0f003a524', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.88,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.28,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. This peer mentor measures decisions by who they might upset and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. In a pinch adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has — without an audience, remembers everyone birthday and no one boundaries.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.74},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.6},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.88,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. This peer mentor measures decisions by who they might upset and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. In a pinch adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has — without an audience, remembers everyone birthday and no one boundaries.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('2b1f5f1a-eaec-4617-b234-d7cdab0c13a4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.92,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.51,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Neighborhood connector whose defining move is that they would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Recharges by being around people, not away from them. The instant it becomes irreversible, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; laughs first to test whether the room is safe to laugh.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.72},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.68}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.92,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Neighborhood connector whose defining move is that they would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Recharges by being around people, not away from them. The instant it becomes irreversible, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; laughs first to test whether the room is safe to laugh.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('50af9c86-e70b-464d-ac10-3d91397b6d9c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.38},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.3,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady unofficial group historian who would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; once the urgency drains out, can sense a mood shift from the doorway.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.55},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.61}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","cognition","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.38}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','cognition','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady unofficial group historian who would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; once the urgency drains out, can sense a mood shift from the doorway.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('cdde3833-a25d-43ea-b1d6-af37e4198cbb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.82,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.24,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When there is no clean exit, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a steady event host who would rather lose a point than win an argument badly and reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and left to their own devices laughs first to test whether the room is safe to laugh.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.61},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.56},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.63},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.59}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.82,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'When there is no clean exit, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a steady event host who would rather lose a point than win an argument badly and reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and left to their own devices laughs first to test whether the room is safe to laugh.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('a2c45e3a-e2a6-4ac8-876b-845e7ab893f4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.47},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.48,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.3,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Group-chat ringleader, pronounced in style: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own; dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Under pressure adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.58},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.69}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.47}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Group-chat ringleader, pronounced in style: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own; dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Under pressure adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
