('24bdf680-9043-458b-9d18-352096fd1d00', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.92,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.66},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.32,"narcissism":0.73,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.31,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Options seller, pronounced in style: recharges by being around people, not away from them; treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. The instant the deadline moves up gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.71},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.76},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.79}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.92,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.66}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Options seller, pronounced in style: recharges by being around people, not away from them; treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. The instant the deadline moves up gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('252ead44-a2a9-4445-9570-626f39142e13', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.53,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady commodities speculator who fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. When the stakes rise finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; when the pressure is off, exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady commodities speculator who fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. When the stakes rise finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; when the pressure is off, exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.92, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('b1990a96-ef20-481d-978d-39cf41bcba88', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.66,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.27,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Family peacemaker, pronounced in style: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely; gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. When someone is watching the outcome adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.56},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.63},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.73},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.61}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","temperament","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.66,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','temperament','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Family peacemaker, pronounced in style: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely; gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. When someone is watching the outcome adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('75f13fc2-bb78-4e7b-ac2f-0cd3041692c1', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.82,"neuroticism":0.33},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.49,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady online moderator who would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Once the exit narrows to one door takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; in the version no one reviews, remembers who didn''t get invited last time.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.59},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.65},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.65},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.77}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","ipip-neo","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.82,"neuroticism":0.33}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','ipip-neo','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady online moderator who would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Once the exit narrows to one door takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; in the version no one reviews, remembers who didn''t get invited last time.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('b31565ff-8012-4b03-badc-4512d2481831', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.41},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.51,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.23,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. This team captain measures decisions by who they might upset and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. The moment it stops being hypothetical finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — left to their own devices, over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.54},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.59},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.62},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.65}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","cognition","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.41}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','cognition','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. This team captain measures decisions by who they might upset and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. The moment it stops being hypothetical finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — left to their own devices, over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.', 0.93, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('af8a76a8-cd66-42fd-87b2-878abc93d99c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.47,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. A steady airdrop farmer: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working, dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and when no one is watching names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.59},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.72},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","open-minded","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','open-minded','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. A steady airdrop farmer: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working, dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and when no one is watching names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('fb436b8c-d111-46ab-896a-1d4b128e794a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.63},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.41,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. This commodities speculator fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to and reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. When the number turns red cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long — in the routine of it, talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.66},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.63}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. This commodities speculator fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to and reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. When the number turns red cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long — in the routine of it, talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.95, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('ca1f0339-39d5-436e-a1f4-02eab2d38125', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.47},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.55,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. A steady index-fund holdout: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to, absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and in the small things sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.47}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. A steady index-fund holdout: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to, absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and in the small things sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.95, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('692c33b9-875a-4e27-8151-ed2f293a0041', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.81,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.56,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.51,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Community manager whose defining move is that they apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. When the downside gets concrete, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; says yes out loud and no internally.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.57},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.72},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.59}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.81,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Community manager whose defining move is that they apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. When the downside gets concrete, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; says yes out loud and no internally.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('49a86c53-190b-4b56-a0ce-fc7a40dfa646', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.63},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.51,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. This futures spreader dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Under pressure finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — across an ordinary week, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.81}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.63}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. This futures spreader dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Under pressure finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — across an ordinary week, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('42845aa7-d7ae-4c2f-b9a0-96306c1ee57d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.49,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.27,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady social-media strategist who absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; on a slow afternoon, laughs first to test whether the room is safe to laugh.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.63},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.64}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","risk","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','risk','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady social-media strategist who absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; on a slow afternoon, laughs first to test whether the room is safe to laugh.', 0.95, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('d80251b4-36c7-477d-b286-9b0c576b679e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.24,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When the walls close in, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When the walls close in, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('552286b0-9d50-48a7-ada8-f5df0bd67850', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.79,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.4,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The instant it becomes irreversible, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. Otherwise, a pronounced community manager who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision and measures decisions by who they might upset. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and in the version no one reviews reads the room then performs to it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.72},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.65},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.55},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.62}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","outgoing","ipip-neo","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.79,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','outgoing','ipip-neo','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'The instant it becomes irreversible, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. Otherwise, a pronounced community manager who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision and measures decisions by who they might upset. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and in the version no one reviews reads the room then performs to it.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('c0fbb2d8-6f5b-4e23-8bd5-56ea701fad2b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.97,"neuroticism":0.47},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.31,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.4,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. A pronounced unofficial group historian: apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault, treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and across the quiet stretches over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.72},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.67},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.69},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.77}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.97,"neuroticism":0.47}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. A pronounced unofficial group historian: apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault, treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and across the quiet stretches over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('e03e6c7a-740a-45e2-a4dc-234b3ad073c3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.54,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Once things get tense gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; in the routine of it, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.73},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Once things get tense gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; in the routine of it, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('03ba42d0-feb8-46f7-b777-96ec778e2ad6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.44,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Reluctant plus-one whose defining move is that they dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. When the stakes rise, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; defuses tension with a joke that lands most of the time.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.65},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.71},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.53},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.59}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","outgoing","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','outgoing','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Reluctant plus-one whose defining move is that they dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. When the stakes rise, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; defuses tension with a joke that lands most of the time.', 0.88, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('9d405c9d-517e-4c6a-bbf0-e8ffe3525372', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.27,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Discretionary swing trader whose defining move is that they draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. The instant the deadline moves up, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.75},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Discretionary swing trader whose defining move is that they draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. The instant the deadline moves up, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
