('441e4db6-e37b-4396-b1d9-e4effa43f4bd', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.24,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A pronounced dividend-yield chaser: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades, dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and when no one is watching refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.72},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.72},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","open-minded","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','open-minded','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A pronounced dividend-yield chaser: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades, dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and when no one is watching refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('3abf2f83-d89f-4a0c-a959-7af1d898ef0d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.67},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.33,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.28,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady discretionary swing trader who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. The instant the deadline moves up discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; across an ordinary week, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.72},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","open-minded","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.67}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','open-minded','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady discretionary swing trader who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. The instant the deadline moves up discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; across an ordinary week, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.95, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('0e2c5c52-21b7-4013-a22f-1124315bf72a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.93,"agreeableness":0.8,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.77,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.55,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Under pressure, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. Otherwise, a pronounced crypto day-trader who fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and when no one is watching apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.84},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.93,"agreeableness":0.8,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Under pressure, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. Otherwise, a pronounced crypto day-trader who fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and when no one is watching apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('3a22f626-809a-4155-8c33-bd2f65be62ed', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.81,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.27,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady community manager who treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Measures decisions by who they might upset. In a pinch abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; when no one is watching, reads the room then performs to it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.56},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.8},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.64},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","outgoing","decision-making","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.81,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','outgoing','decision-making','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady community manager who treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Measures decisions by who they might upset. In a pinch abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; when no one is watching, reads the room then performs to it.', 0.95, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('33c79b2a-7718-43ab-a194-0a3e1869c628', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.79,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.33,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.25,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the number turns red, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a steady retail momentum chaser who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and in the pattern nobody else tracks holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.7},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.79,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'When the number turns red, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a steady retail momentum chaser who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and in the pattern nobody else tracks holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('814df750-a569-40e5-b71a-80eb086b50ee', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.33,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Meme-coin rotator, pronounced in style: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to; apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. When the stakes rise finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.7},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.56},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Meme-coin rotator, pronounced in style: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to; apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. When the stakes rise finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('ca3dc57b-646e-46cb-acbf-9b502306b6a2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.44,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Airdrop farmer, steady in style: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to; reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Once the exit narrows to one door gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.78}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Airdrop farmer, steady in style: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to; reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Once the exit narrows to one door gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('ca8ff4fe-a4ca-458b-8273-958ec631e10e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.82,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.39,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady team captain who treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Once things get tense gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; in the routine of it, over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.71},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.59},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.6}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","outgoing","behavioral","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.82,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','outgoing','behavioral','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady team captain who treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Once things get tense gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; in the routine of it, over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('64133ac1-b092-4c74-9a92-ae852e311ed3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.66},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.52,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A steady crypto day-trader: draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone, absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and in the version no one reviews checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.7},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.68},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.74},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.66}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A steady crypto day-trader: draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone, absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and in the version no one reviews checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.91, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('0195f382-155a-4c06-8bf6-a7d86fbc105d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.49,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.81,"neuroticism":0.42},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.31,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.34,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Wedding-party diplomat, steady in style: absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost; recharges by being around people, not away from them. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. When the downside gets concrete adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.71},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.57},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.63},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.81}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","cognition","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.49,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.81,"neuroticism":0.42}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','cognition','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Wedding-party diplomat, steady in style: absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost; recharges by being around people, not away from them. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. When the downside gets concrete adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.', 0.92, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('27c03fd9-8fc9-494e-bdaf-6506464c1fd9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.23,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When there is no clean exit, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. Otherwise, a pronounced MEV searcher who treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved and starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and in the pattern nobody else tracks holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.72},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.61},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'When there is no clean exit, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. Otherwise, a pronounced MEV searcher who treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved and starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and in the pattern nobody else tracks holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('1def3670-40bc-4357-807c-570bf7c91ff0', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.9,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.23,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the number turns red, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. Otherwise, a pronounced group-chat ringleader who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely and over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and when no one is watching laughs first to test whether the room is safe to laugh.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.72},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.77},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.59},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.66}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.9,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'When the number turns red, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. Otherwise, a pronounced group-chat ringleader who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely and over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and when no one is watching laughs first to test whether the room is safe to laugh.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('b1111389-81c5-4f66-9b9f-32330f928a94', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.63},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.44,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. This onchain copy-trader treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved and reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. The moment risk appears takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis — in the small things, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.68},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.62},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.63}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. This onchain copy-trader treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved and reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. The moment risk appears takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis — in the small things, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('e694050c-41f6-4895-9538-62c87f5212a6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.83,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.32,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.29,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady group-project default leader who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; across an ordinary week, mediates conflicts they secretly started.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.64},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.53},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.63}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.83,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady group-project default leader who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; across an ordinary week, mediates conflicts they secretly started.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('a89240aa-09f9-44db-a1eb-7e6f0f2d0b1b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.89,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.44,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced longtime regular at the same three places who takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. When cornered takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; in the version no one reviews, can sense a mood shift from the doorway.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.8},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.84}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","behavioral","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.89,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','behavioral','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A pronounced longtime regular at the same three places who takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. When cornered takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; in the version no one reviews, can sense a mood shift from the doorway.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('95eb610a-7922-44ab-981a-d68c0d13f6f2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.51,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.43,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. This reluctant plus-one absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Once the exit narrows to one door finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view — in the version no one reviews, can sense a mood shift from the doorway.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.57},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.56},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.55}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","behavioral","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','behavioral','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. This reluctant plus-one absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Once the exit narrows to one door finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view — in the version no one reviews, can sense a mood shift from the doorway.', 0.93, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('f5f8127d-ab52-4f1f-b0b5-76f94c08ac37', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.85,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.33,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.4,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Longtime regular at the same three places whose defining move is that they reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; texts an apology before confirming anyone is upset.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.78},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.58}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.85,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Longtime regular at the same three places whose defining move is that they reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; texts an apology before confirming anyone is upset.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('82ade1bf-2f52-4375-ab2b-9e1bd2d64933', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.94,"agreeableness":0.82,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.77,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.52,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Dividend-yield chaser whose defining move is that they recharges by being around people, not away from them. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. The moment risk appears, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.82},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.89}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.94,"agreeableness":0.82,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Dividend-yield chaser whose defining move is that they recharges by being around people, not away from them. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. The moment risk appears, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('29131ccb-8e87-4b9b-8589-5e19bfb1df94', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.62},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.53,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Quant researcher whose defining move is that they draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. When cornered, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.75},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.78}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.62}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Quant researcher whose defining move is that they draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. When cornered, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('81daeada-8ca7-4265-bf97-5327d73cbb51', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.54,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Peer mentor, steady in style: absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost; thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Under a deadline gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.63},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.6},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","cognition","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','cognition','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Peer mentor, steady in style: absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost; thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Under a deadline gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it.', 0.88, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('008c80c7-8607-45a2-86ec-1d6e1121b6aa', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.65,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.83,"neuroticism":0.41},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.31,"alpha":0.95,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady group-project default leader who takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. The instant it becomes irreversible gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; in the small things, remembers who didn''t get invited last time.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.82},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.64},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.81}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.65,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.83,"neuroticism":0.41}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady group-project default leader who takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. The instant it becomes irreversible gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; in the small things, remembers who didn''t get invited last time.', 0.93, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('326d79bf-42ac-4e53-9efd-ae54bff50679', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.54,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A steady prop-desk scalper: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision, chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and in the routine of it checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.71},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A steady prop-desk scalper: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision, chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and in the routine of it checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('9163d72c-9702-4e1b-bba0-847cea56bb36', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.47,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Algorithmic market-maker, steady in style: draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone; is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. The moment risk appears finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.6},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Algorithmic market-maker, steady in style: draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone; is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. The moment risk appears finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.', 0.91, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('27eb4c85-e632-4e26-9c84-20ae20bff31f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.71,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.91,"neuroticism":0.47},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.36,"alpha":0.95,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Group-project default leader, pronounced in style: apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault; thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. When someone is watching the outcome adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.62},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.76},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.81}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","decision-making","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.71,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.91,"neuroticism":0.47}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','decision-making','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Group-project default leader, pronounced in style: apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault; thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. When someone is watching the outcome adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('4ade373a-0bac-4d36-a0d1-cc977c75a96a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.86,"neuroticism":0.37},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.29,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When there is no clean exit, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. Otherwise, a pronounced longtime regular at the same three places who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault and treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and when the stakes are trivial remembers who didn''t get invited last time.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.79},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.62},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.71}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.86,"neuroticism":0.37}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'When there is no clean exit, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. Otherwise, a pronounced longtime regular at the same three places who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault and treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and when the stakes are trivial remembers who didn''t get invited last time.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('c24aa36a-f707-4b25-8b30-ed5823ef9059', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.93,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.55,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced bonding-curve sniper who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. The instant it becomes irreversible adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; when the pressure is off, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.77},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.78}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.93,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A pronounced bonding-curve sniper who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. The instant it becomes irreversible adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; when the pressure is off, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('f1c62b44-7ee4-4880-803a-a2ee0fcb3943', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.28,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A pronounced pairs trader: dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet, absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and left to their own devices backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.73},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A pronounced pairs trader: dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet, absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and left to their own devices backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('955b4051-6e5e-4927-9f9e-57f9fd968cac', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.53,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.53,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The friend who always drives, steady in style: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely; recharges by being around people, not away from them. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. The moment it stops being hypothetical abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.66},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.59},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.61},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.58}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'The friend who always drives, steady in style: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely; recharges by being around people, not away from them. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. The moment it stops being hypothetical abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.', 0.93, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('b75d80f6-57f0-478f-996b-40e8cc1d5067', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.66,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.29,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the number turns red, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. Otherwise, a pronounced unofficial group historian who takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and once the urgency drains out keeps a mental ledger of social debts.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.62},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.76}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.66,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'When the number turns red, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. Otherwise, a pronounced unofficial group historian who takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and once the urgency drains out keeps a mental ledger of social debts.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('4adb6fcb-033a-4211-8c35-950e072c9ad3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.55,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Value investor whose defining move is that they thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Value investor whose defining move is that they thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.89, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('9dc32c64-3aa4-409f-9a48-af565e1ebd78', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.49,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady crypto day-trader who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. The instant the deadline moves up finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; on a slow afternoon, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.59},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.6},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","open-minded","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','open-minded','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady crypto day-trader who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. The instant the deadline moves up finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; on a slow afternoon, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('a80561a9-7d58-4a17-8efa-fbf2002df349', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.97,"neuroticism":0.45},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.37,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Unofficial group historian whose defining move is that they takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Once the exit narrows to one door, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; remembers everyone birthday and no one boundaries.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.59},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.73},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.79},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.73}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","decision-making","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.97,"neuroticism":0.45}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','decision-making','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Unofficial group historian whose defining move is that they takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Once the exit narrows to one door, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; remembers everyone birthday and no one boundaries.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('39a0fd34-5b23-4af3-a722-2a18d029b0cc', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.68,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.53,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.49,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The friend who always drives, pronounced in style: reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it; treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. When there is no clean exit abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.66},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.76},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.69}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.68,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'The friend who always drives, pronounced in style: reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it; treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. When there is no clean exit abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.', 0.92, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('25e84197-a9a9-4e55-ba98-eba2394765b5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.77,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.4,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Futures spreader whose defining move is that they recharges by being around people, not away from them. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. The moment risk appears, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.64},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Futures spreader whose defining move is that they recharges by being around people, not away from them. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. The moment risk appears, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('b3cf0030-57dd-49b7-826e-9917741dfb2e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.62,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.51,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Value investor whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. When the downside gets concrete, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.72},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.53},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","open-minded","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','open-minded','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Value investor whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. When the downside gets concrete, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.89, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('69bad4fd-a475-4aef-a060-14fc5ac31625', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.27,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. A pronounced airdrop farmer: treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved, chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and left to their own devices calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.68},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.73},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.69},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.77}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. A pronounced airdrop farmer: treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved, chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and left to their own devices calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.93, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('3c7b0ce2-b916-4699-8bc5-1167accabee9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.33,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.29,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Macro allocator, steady in style: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to; would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. When the walls close in finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Macro allocator, steady in style: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to; would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. When the walls close in finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.', 0.91, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('3ad1579c-a075-4f89-bdcf-7e6976f06bc5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.44,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. This discretionary swing trader reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. When cornered adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has — in the small things, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.58},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","open-minded","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','open-minded','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. This discretionary swing trader reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. When cornered adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has — in the small things, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('200b07bb-62f0-4ffa-95fd-fa782db8e130', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.87,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.52,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Under pressure, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a pronounced the one who remembers everyone''s order who would rather lose a point than win an argument badly and recharges by being around people, not away from them. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and left to their own devices texts an apology before confirming anyone is upset.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.69},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.79},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.8},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.87,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Under pressure, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a pronounced the one who remembers everyone''s order who would rather lose a point than win an argument badly and recharges by being around people, not away from them. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and left to their own devices texts an apology before confirming anyone is upset.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
