('92b53653-ab08-4c62-9bd5-2a9092635e39', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.76,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.32,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.48,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. This discretionary swing trader fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to and reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. The moment it stops being hypothetical finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — without an audience, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.77},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.76,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. This discretionary swing trader fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to and reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. The moment it stops being hypothetical finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — without an audience, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('c0dd1f44-f476-4bb7-943a-5b23488b16b4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.71,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.81,"neuroticism":0.4},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.44,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A steady event host: reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it, reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and in the parts nobody grades reads the room then performs to it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.65},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.64},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.58},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.66}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.71,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.81,"neuroticism":0.4}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A steady event host: reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it, reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and in the parts nobody grades reads the room then performs to it.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('7f7cdc69-5982-492a-9dbb-8482ce9954bb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.48,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Crypto day-trader, steady in style: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision; collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Once the exit narrows to one door treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.62},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Crypto day-trader, steady in style: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision; collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Once the exit narrows to one door treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss.', 0.91, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('fcfd2fa4-e33e-4a18-a219-eab80a584ce2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.87,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.32,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.3,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced liquidation-bot operator who would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Under a deadline adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; day to day, averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.64},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.84},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.77},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","accommodating","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.87,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','accommodating','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A pronounced liquidation-bot operator who would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Under a deadline adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; day to day, averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('bdbc461a-c89a-4568-83c0-8f2df57254b2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.3,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Index-fund holdout, pronounced in style: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to; is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Index-fund holdout, pronounced in style: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to; is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('079f35b4-fc25-418f-aa05-c3822bd779fd', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.62,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.54,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. This neighborhood connector takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own and builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis — in the parts nobody grades, over-commits to plans they later dread.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.68},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.76}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","cognition","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','cognition','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. This neighborhood connector takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own and builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis — in the parts nobody grades, over-commits to plans they later dread.', 0.93, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('1320fef6-11a0-499f-ae5e-8978670ae6a2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.89,"neuroticism":0.45},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.35,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced the friend who always drives who would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. When there is no clean exit adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; when the stakes are trivial, keeps score of favors without meaning to.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.6},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.65},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.77},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.81}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.89,"neuroticism":0.45}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A pronounced the friend who always drives who would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. When there is no clean exit adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; when the stakes are trivial, keeps score of favors without meaning to.', 0.95, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('dc41b072-9626-424a-be4e-6cefb64e08e9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.68,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.9,"neuroticism":0.45},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.52,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.55,"alpha":0.96,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. This neighborhood connector would rather lose a point than win an argument badly and narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — across the quiet stretches, texts an apology before confirming anyone is upset.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.76},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.64},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.67},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.58}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.68,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.9,"neuroticism":0.45}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. This neighborhood connector would rather lose a point than win an argument badly and narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — across the quiet stretches, texts an apology before confirming anyone is upset.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
