('867bf488-1310-4f16-8cd7-8b9f5db99381', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.96,"neuroticism":0.38},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.32,"narcissism":0.54,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.48,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. This online moderator reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Under pressure gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it — in the small things, reads the room then performs to it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.8},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.65}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","temperament","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.96,"neuroticism":0.38}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','temperament','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. This online moderator reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Under pressure gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it — in the small things, reads the room then performs to it.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('5840ad88-82a1-4c00-a966-f23fbcac23db', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.31,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"In a pinch, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a steady onchain copy-trader who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision and collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and when no one is watching sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.76},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'In a pinch, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a steady onchain copy-trader who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision and collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and when no one is watching sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.95, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('8d23c8f2-63fc-4f13-b54f-1830bc6c95f5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.7,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.87,"neuroticism":0.47},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.5,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Social-media strategist, pronounced in style: absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost; treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Under a deadline adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.8}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","behavioral","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.7,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.87,"neuroticism":0.47}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','behavioral','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Social-media strategist, pronounced in style: absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost; treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Under a deadline adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('972e76da-6033-4458-8aa3-1b2b4c1a1013', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.97,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.83,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.5,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Value investor, pronounced in style: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to; treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Once things get tense finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.87},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.97,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Value investor, pronounced in style: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to; treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Once things get tense finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('5c0c9ef1-4cc7-4b59-b1f7-3adb7d0cc105', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.91,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.73,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.42,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced liquidation-bot operator who recharges by being around people, not away from them. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Once things get tense finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; on a slow afternoon, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.85},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.84}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.91,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A pronounced liquidation-bot operator who recharges by being around people, not away from them. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Once things get tense finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; on a slow afternoon, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('47159893-54c2-43a2-b310-83ecfab9ee01', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.83,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.31,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady online moderator who measures decisions by who they might upset. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. When cornered gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; day to day, drafts the apology before the mistake.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.56},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.8},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.59},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.59}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","behavioral","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.83,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','behavioral','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady online moderator who measures decisions by who they might upset. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. When cornered gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; day to day, drafts the apology before the mistake.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('822e9d7a-598b-4df4-bbae-0383344a9a7f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.62,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.54,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced unofficial group historian who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. When the number turns red finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; when the stakes are trivial, can sense a mood shift from the doorway.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.79},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.64}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","temperament","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','temperament','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A pronounced unofficial group historian who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. When the number turns red finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; when the stakes are trivial, can sense a mood shift from the doorway.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('a05fea4d-8e35-48e1-b2cd-cf40afd5b3cf', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.23,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Liquidation-bot operator whose defining move is that they treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. The instant the deadline moves up, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.62},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.71},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Liquidation-bot operator whose defining move is that they treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. The instant the deadline moves up, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('e6a1d0be-9362-4651-97c6-47e0265b29e5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.8,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.54,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.35,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. This newcomer welcomer would rather lose a point than win an argument badly and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. The instant it becomes irreversible adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has — day to day, remembers everyone birthday and no one boundaries.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.61},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.71}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","cognition","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.8,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','cognition','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. This newcomer welcomer would rather lose a point than win an argument badly and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. The instant it becomes irreversible adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has — day to day, remembers everyone birthday and no one boundaries.', 0.93, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('a24868ce-e811-4ffd-a231-f9b5930ce5e9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.46,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. This liquidation-bot operator collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. When there is no clean exit adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has — in the parts nobody grades, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.67},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","open-minded","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','open-minded','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. This liquidation-bot operator collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. When there is no clean exit adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has — in the parts nobody grades, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.92, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('6d353300-46fc-48f2-94e4-3b4f20bb1d9a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.23,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Onchain copy-trader whose defining move is that they narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Once the exit narrows to one door, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery; keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.76},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Onchain copy-trader whose defining move is that they narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Once the exit narrows to one door, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery; keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.95, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('302c3e29-f030-4323-a4d1-c8c5484738b8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.42},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.56,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. This community manager defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. The moment risk appears abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way — across an ordinary week, over-commits to plans they later dread.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.67},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.6},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.42}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. This community manager defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. The moment risk appears abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way — across an ordinary week, over-commits to plans they later dread.', 0.95, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('e2cdc2ff-3a48-47bc-94ad-f7cac758a475', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.5,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The moment risk appears, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a pronounced bonding-curve sniper who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and across the quiet stretches exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.58},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.77},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.64},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'The moment risk appears, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a pronounced bonding-curve sniper who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and across the quiet stretches exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('64d7aa7e-ff29-4910-a2e6-ef99f5c69b19', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.5,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady airdrop farmer who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. The moment it stops being hypothetical treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; when the stakes are trivial, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.67},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady airdrop farmer who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. The moment it stops being hypothetical treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; when the stakes are trivial, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.93, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('cffa8e9b-f041-44a2-87e6-092bf9b0d298', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.89,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.35,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A pronounced the one who remembers everyone''s order: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own, reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and on an ordinary week over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.77},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.73}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.89,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A pronounced the one who remembers everyone''s order: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own, reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and on an ordinary week over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('4ca671d8-7e7a-426f-8685-ea71561073ad', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.8,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.53,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Newcomer welcomer whose defining move is that they thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. When the safe option quietly expires, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; texts an apology before confirming anyone is upset.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.63},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.63},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.7},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.62}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","outgoing","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.8,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','outgoing','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Newcomer welcomer whose defining move is that they thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. When the safe option quietly expires, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; texts an apology before confirming anyone is upset.', 0.92, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('d4706842-d78e-48db-8bcd-a7ff9941efe2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.86,"neuroticism":0.39},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.57,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Nonprofit convener, pronounced in style: would rather lose a point than win an argument badly; draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. When the number turns red gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.65},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.74}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.86,"neuroticism":0.39}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Nonprofit convener, pronounced in style: would rather lose a point than win an argument badly; draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. When the number turns red gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('c7a01e98-c0ed-4270-b866-6b533ec6e436', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.95,"agreeableness":0.76,"neuroticism":0.65},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.56,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Bonding-curve sniper whose defining move is that they narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. The instant the deadline moves up, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.73},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.6},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.83},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.8}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.95,"agreeableness":0.76,"neuroticism":0.65}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Bonding-curve sniper whose defining move is that they narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. The instant the deadline moves up, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('6fbdfb1c-69b5-4bf3-8d1e-fe903a2bfa05', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.88,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.55,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the stakes rise, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a pronounced group-chat ringleader who reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it and treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and in the pattern nobody else tracks keeps score of favors without meaning to.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.64},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.68}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","behavioral","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.88,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','behavioral','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'When the stakes rise, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a pronounced group-chat ringleader who reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it and treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and in the pattern nobody else tracks keeps score of favors without meaning to.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
