('e91c31c5-b87c-4d09-bd06-41a26addb53c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.79,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.31,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.46,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Quant researcher whose defining move is that they dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. The moment risk appears, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.75},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.71},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.79,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Quant researcher whose defining move is that they dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. The moment risk appears, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('6a1fe30c-7b94-4cdd-a349-570451d94343', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.63},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.32,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.53,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The moment it stops being hypothetical, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. Otherwise, a pronounced penny-stock gambler who narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it and collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and in the version no one reviews talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.8},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.8},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.63}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'The moment it stops being hypothetical, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. Otherwise, a pronounced penny-stock gambler who narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it and collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and in the version no one reviews talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('4bd0f9fa-e95c-4692-9849-ed0926f6e984', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.66,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.83,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.24,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Neighborhood connector whose defining move is that they defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. When the downside gets concrete, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.7},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.66,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.83,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Neighborhood connector whose defining move is that they defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. When the downside gets concrete, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('f04d2b1f-4d02-468d-9038-5cf195bd5f89', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.33,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.48,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced onchain copy-trader who fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; on a slow afternoon, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.65},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.7},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.56},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A pronounced onchain copy-trader who fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; on a slow afternoon, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('8b034fd7-0c16-4d69-ad7e-1a4b5599e5f7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.47,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Bonding-curve sniper, steady in style: dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet; would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Once the exit narrows to one door adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.58},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Bonding-curve sniper, steady in style: dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet; would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Once the exit narrows to one door adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.', 0.89, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('34893c3a-ca02-4ae9-b296-7f3e6a14a98d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.83,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.32,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.41,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. A pronounced liquidation-bot operator: recharges by being around people, not away from them, would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and in the parts nobody grades keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.83},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.8},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.69},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.83,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. A pronounced liquidation-bot operator: recharges by being around people, not away from them, would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and in the parts nobody grades keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('26be514e-f2cc-41f4-b2cc-8b9dddfac905', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.27,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"MEV searcher whose defining move is that they recharges by being around people, not away from them. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. The instant the deadline moves up, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.77},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.8}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'MEV searcher whose defining move is that they recharges by being around people, not away from them. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. The instant the deadline moves up, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.95, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('ead18590-f2d2-4614-9bf8-c3d52767dcbb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.82,"neuroticism":0.35},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.48,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Longtime regular at the same three places, steady in style: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own; gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. When cornered finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.63},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.68},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.59}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.82,"neuroticism":0.35}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Longtime regular at the same three places, steady in style: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own; gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. When cornered finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view.', 0.93, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('b7c9ef22-5ed3-4448-95a1-3030b7c948e8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.49,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced airdrop farmer who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. When the number turns red abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; on an ordinary week, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.72},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A pronounced airdrop farmer who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. When the number turns red abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; on an ordinary week, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.95, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('8801b308-d429-486c-949c-d3d45bcbad94', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.31,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.32,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A pronounced peer mentor: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own, treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and across the quiet stretches can sense a mood shift from the doorway.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.68},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.77}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","ipip-neo","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','ipip-neo','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A pronounced peer mentor: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own, treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and across the quiet stretches can sense a mood shift from the doorway.', 0.93, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('5d59329c-8faf-4e79-9299-39e7b105c4d3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.25,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When cornered, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. Otherwise, a steady macro allocator who treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved and absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and as a rule backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.75},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'When cornered, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. Otherwise, a steady macro allocator who treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved and absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and as a rule backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.89, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('17264bcb-11d7-4693-af1f-730dcf48ee91', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.43,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. A pronounced pairs trader: treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved, carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and in the routine of it treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.74},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.68},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.78}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. A pronounced pairs trader: treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved, carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and in the routine of it treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.95, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('973f2bbd-f8de-409e-8598-d8dfdb8f210c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.33,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.44,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Futures spreader, steady in style: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working; takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. When the number turns red abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.68},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.77},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","open-minded","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','open-minded','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Futures spreader, steady in style: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working; takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. When the number turns red abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.', 0.89, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('4c80b318-1a9d-4c60-b271-7636f464f6a5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.86,"neuroticism":0.45},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.46,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"In a pinch, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. Otherwise, a pronounced the friend who always drives who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and in the parts nobody grades defuses tension with a joke that lands most of the time.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.65},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.64},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.81},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.58}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.86,"neuroticism":0.45}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'In a pinch, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. Otherwise, a pronounced the friend who always drives who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and in the parts nobody grades defuses tension with a joke that lands most of the time.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('1574a8e9-085e-454b-aa6e-0fb51e96400b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.82,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.33,"narcissism":0.48,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.5,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When someone is watching the outcome, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. Otherwise, a steady community manager who takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own and narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and in the routine of it laughs first to test whether the room is safe to laugh.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.68},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.64}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","behavioral","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.82,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','behavioral','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'When someone is watching the outcome, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. Otherwise, a steady community manager who takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own and narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and in the routine of it laughs first to test whether the room is safe to laugh.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('02c48ee3-a7b1-425a-a11e-3d01c35e9707', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.91,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.53,"psychopathy":0.25},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.23,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced group-project default leader who reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. The instant it becomes irreversible gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; on a slow afternoon, remembers who didn''t get invited last time.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.71},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.65},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.62},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.75}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.91,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A pronounced group-project default leader who reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. The instant it becomes irreversible gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; on a slow afternoon, remembers who didn''t get invited last time.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('1eb3ae77-573a-4243-a687-342c607f003a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.85,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.5,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.45,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the stakes rise, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. Otherwise, a pronounced group-chat ringleader who absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and day to day laughs first to test whether the room is safe to laugh.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.63},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.85,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'When the stakes rise, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. Otherwise, a pronounced group-chat ringleader who absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and day to day laughs first to test whether the room is safe to laugh.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('4b4510d2-e181-4c3a-a318-fc5f79558ee5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.76,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.56,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A steady community manager: would rather lose a point than win an argument badly, would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and in the small things defuses tension with a joke that lands most of the time.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.65},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","behavioral","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.76,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','behavioral','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A steady community manager: would rather lose a point than win an argument badly, would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and in the small things defuses tension with a joke that lands most of the time.', 0.91, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('aef94fce-080c-475a-b238-6f5a2a055170', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.42,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"In a pinch, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a steady MEV searcher who fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to and apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and when the pressure is off averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.68},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'In a pinch, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a steady MEV searcher who fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to and apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and when the pressure is off averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('6cb7a1a7-4fb6-46c7-8e11-2330da67d8c2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.96,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.82,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.5,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"In a pinch, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a pronounced airdrop farmer who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and day to day refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.74},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.84}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.96,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'In a pinch, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a pronounced airdrop farmer who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and day to day refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('a6a52d0d-50b8-4f34-b5d9-1b346fc38e5b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.65,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.86,"neuroticism":0.39},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.47,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The one who remembers everyone''s order, pronounced in style: reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it; maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Under a deadline finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.6},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.79},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.68}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","temperament","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.65,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.86,"neuroticism":0.39}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','temperament','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'The one who remembers everyone''s order, pronounced in style: reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it; maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Under a deadline finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
