('caa1e6b9-f127-4004-9c80-0ac0d69b81b7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.45},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.35,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. This nonprofit convener collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and recharges by being around people, not away from them. Once the exit narrows to one door gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it — on a slow afternoon, keeps score of favors without meaning to.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.57},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.61},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.53},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.49}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","open-minded","risk","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.45}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','open-minded','risk','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. This nonprofit convener collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and recharges by being around people, not away from them. Once the exit narrows to one door gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it — on a slow afternoon, keeps score of favors without meaning to.', 0.86, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('e8dfcbd1-f431-4797-87be-0e48f399d27d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.83,"neuroticism":0.47},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.3,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Community manager whose defining move is that they defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. When the walls close in, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; remembers who didn''t get invited last time.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.78},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.77}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","ipip-neo","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.83,"neuroticism":0.47}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','ipip-neo','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Community manager whose defining move is that they defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. When the walls close in, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; remembers who didn''t get invited last time.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('ab51a4f8-7343-40ab-a806-ef3eb4041804', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.65,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.86,"neuroticism":0.45},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.24,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. This community manager absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost and reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Under a deadline adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has — without an audience, over-commits to plans they later dread.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.8}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","ipip-neo","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.65,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.86,"neuroticism":0.45}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','ipip-neo','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. This community manager absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost and reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Under a deadline adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has — without an audience, over-commits to plans they later dread.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
