('e5978ed3-ff3d-4353-9e5a-22c45921c564', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.68},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.33,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.55,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. A steady macro allocator: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades, needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and on an ordinary week sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","open-minded","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.68}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','open-minded','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. A steady macro allocator: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades, needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and on an ordinary week sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.9, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('6a61d483-930a-443d-8501-1824f79b7d63', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.33,"narcissism":0.62,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.28,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. This index-fund holdout draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone and gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Under a deadline takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis — across the quiet stretches, talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.79},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.77}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. This index-fund holdout draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone and gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Under a deadline takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis — across the quiet stretches, talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('189a6558-828c-4bc5-ba19-3d49aff46d2c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.86,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.25},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.3,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. A pronounced the one who remembers everyone''s order: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely, gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and on an ordinary week over-commits to plans they later dread.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.62},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.67},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.78}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.86,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. A pronounced the one who remembers everyone''s order: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely, gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and on an ordinary week over-commits to plans they later dread.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('40a2e041-e57b-46c4-be4b-c49ac25e08e1', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.62},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.51,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A steady bonding-curve sniper: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and day to day apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.68},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.68},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","open-minded","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.62}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','open-minded','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A steady bonding-curve sniper: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and day to day apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.93, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('6ec5e47c-4374-492b-a16c-e01f7176b354', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.92,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.48,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The instant it becomes irreversible, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a pronounced group-chat ringleader who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and when no one is watching defuses tension with a joke that lands most of the time.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.68},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.77}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","behavioral","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.92,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','behavioral','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'The instant it becomes irreversible, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a pronounced group-chat ringleader who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and when no one is watching defuses tension with a joke that lands most of the time.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('20d8e8ec-a19d-41a3-9569-fa43811deabf', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.67,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.29,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady commodities speculator who recharges by being around people, not away from them. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Under a deadline finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; in the routine of it, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.73},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady commodities speculator who recharges by being around people, not away from them. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Under a deadline finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; in the routine of it, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.91, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('717aa522-cf39-4325-ba14-11f43bf7d817', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.74,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.8,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.39,"alpha":0.96,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady reluctant plus-one who would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. When the downside gets concrete finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; across an ordinary week, keeps a mental ledger of social debts.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.65},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.71},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.68}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.74,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.8,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady reluctant plus-one who would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. When the downside gets concrete finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; across an ordinary week, keeps a mental ledger of social debts.', 0.91, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('25467f24-987a-40fd-839b-19846fc1fcbb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.56,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Quant researcher whose defining move is that they draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. When the downside gets concrete, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.71},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.8}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Quant researcher whose defining move is that they draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. When the downside gets concrete, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('a9978a8e-c48e-409c-ad4c-ac4473070b4e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.54,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced airdrop farmer who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. When there is no clean exit finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; left to their own devices, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.75},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.79}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A pronounced airdrop farmer who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. When there is no clean exit finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; left to their own devices, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('87d59ac3-bec7-4a68-a876-350e29ca1a97', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.62},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.26,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady meme-coin rotator who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Under a deadline adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; when no one is watching, apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.65},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.69},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.62}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady meme-coin rotator who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Under a deadline adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; when no one is watching, apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.92, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
