('2fe91174-31a8-46e3-9894-eaf687fdf1d8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.8,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.33,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.31,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Prop-desk scalper, pronounced in style: recharges by being around people, not away from them; defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. When the number turns red finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.82},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.8,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Prop-desk scalper, pronounced in style: recharges by being around people, not away from them; defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. When the number turns red finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('51b82832-917f-4a6b-8d95-39d51c80c17e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.76,"neuroticism":0.62},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.33,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.52,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. A pronounced retail momentum chaser: treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved, chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and without an audience sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.68},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.76}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.76,"neuroticism":0.62}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. A pronounced retail momentum chaser: treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved, chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and without an audience sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('bcad5343-07c0-4fa6-9f77-34502dcd0f6e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.69,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.28,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Liquidation-bot operator whose defining move is that they collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Once things get tense, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","open-minded","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','open-minded','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Liquidation-bot operator whose defining move is that they collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Once things get tense, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('97ac706d-8adb-4eaf-836c-8e1309703dc2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.36},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.41,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Online moderator, steady in style: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely; checks its own anxiety like a data point instead of obeying it. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. When the stakes rise takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.67},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.59}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.36}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Online moderator, steady in style: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely; checks its own anxiety like a data point instead of obeying it. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. When the stakes rise takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis.', 0.91, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('e664e1b7-e9b8-4a59-861c-9aad1a9b25c5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.51,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Volatility arbitrageur, steady in style: dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet; reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. When the walls close in finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.8},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Volatility arbitrageur, steady in style: dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet; reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. When the walls close in finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('4d2caacc-bab9-4b37-be1b-8945d3f0a5a9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.67,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.35,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. This penny-stock gambler dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When someone is watching the outcome takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis — as a rule, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. This penny-stock gambler dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When someone is watching the outcome takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis — as a rule, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('f724d1b8-19db-4743-a84f-1d61c780afd5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.36,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. This onchain copy-trader draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone and chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. When cornered abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way — in the parts nobody grades, exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.62},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. This onchain copy-trader draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone and chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. When cornered abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way — in the parts nobody grades, exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
