('934d8d39-fe71-4b36-a79f-7c9117e92201', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.25,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Prop-desk scalper whose defining move is that they fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. When cornered, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.71},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Prop-desk scalper whose defining move is that they fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. When cornered, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('dd12d0cb-e981-4859-b1ae-918ec008792b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.76,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.25,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"In a pinch, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. Otherwise, a steady team captain who takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and in the unglamorous middle of things remembers everyone birthday and no one boundaries.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.53}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","decision-making","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.76,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','decision-making','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'In a pinch, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. Otherwise, a steady team captain who takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and in the unglamorous middle of things remembers everyone birthday and no one boundaries.', 0.92, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('36296e25-0fc8-47ad-aab3-8e12c6986af1', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.83,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.43,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Longtime regular at the same three places, steady in style: absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost; chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. When the safe option quietly expires adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.78},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.58},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.62}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.83,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Longtime regular at the same three places, steady in style: absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost; chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. When the safe option quietly expires adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('b01d30c9-abba-4a00-93a0-bf5bfa28b60b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.82,"neuroticism":0.47},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.54,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.44,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Nonprofit convener, steady in style: measures decisions by who they might upset; treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Under pressure abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.71},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.57},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.6}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.82,"neuroticism":0.47}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Nonprofit convener, steady in style: measures decisions by who they might upset; treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Under pressure abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('f84f97c8-7707-4db2-85c5-dcf2cdab1cc5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.24,"extraversion":0.97,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.84,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.4,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. This delta-neutral market maker fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to and apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. When cornered is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest — on a slow afternoon, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.8},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.81},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.24,"extraversion":0.97,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. This delta-neutral market maker fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to and apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. When cornered is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest — on a slow afternoon, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('db0f708d-f373-451b-b5f6-66daf09a181c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.86,"neuroticism":0.39},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.53,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the downside gets concrete, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. Otherwise, a pronounced wedding-party diplomat who measures decisions by who they might upset and reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and left to their own devices keeps score of favors without meaning to.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.6},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.69},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.83}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","cognition","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.86,"neuroticism":0.39}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','cognition','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'When the downside gets concrete, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. Otherwise, a pronounced wedding-party diplomat who measures decisions by who they might upset and reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and left to their own devices keeps score of favors without meaning to.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('de504475-6da9-4031-8b90-83b103094e39', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.34},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.46,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A pronounced unofficial group historian: absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost, draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and when no one is watching over-commits to plans they later dread.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.65},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.81},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.71}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","cognition","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.34}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','cognition','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A pronounced unofficial group historian: absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost, draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and when no one is watching over-commits to plans they later dread.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('01064f28-5177-4339-b931-5615d58821cf', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.96,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.57,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. A pronounced penny-stock gambler: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision, takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and without an audience holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.76},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.8}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.96,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. A pronounced penny-stock gambler: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision, takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and without an audience holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('8e463301-1b64-426b-ab5e-63db5104e51f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.76,"neuroticism":0.4},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.51,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.4,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Gives a credentialed opinion more weight than the argument earns. A steady longtime regular at the same three places: measures decisions by who they might upset, thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and across an ordinary week defuses tension with a joke that lands most of the time.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.58},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.63},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.57}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","decision-making","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.76,"neuroticism":0.4}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','decision-making','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Gives a credentialed opinion more weight than the argument earns. A steady longtime regular at the same three places: measures decisions by who they might upset, thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and across an ordinary week defuses tension with a joke that lands most of the time.', 0.93, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('290d5a52-a8ab-43dc-be47-e3b1373692d9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.96,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.79,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.23,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"MEV searcher whose defining move is that they narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Measures decisions by who they might upset. Once things get tense, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.75},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.79}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.96,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'MEV searcher whose defining move is that they narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Measures decisions by who they might upset. Once things get tense, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('05e50c32-d8c0-4588-bf0b-ff91e5a8c74c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.88,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.49,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced reluctant plus-one who reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. When the walls close in finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; day to day, says yes out loud and no internally.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.68},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.71}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.88,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A pronounced reluctant plus-one who reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. When the walls close in finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; day to day, says yes out loud and no internally.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
