('eade5102-198a-4cad-9a5d-7f41b3b779d2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.83,"neuroticism":0.41},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.37,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Peer mentor whose defining move is that they takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. When cornered, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; texts an apology before confirming anyone is upset.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.59},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.83,"neuroticism":0.41}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Peer mentor whose defining move is that they takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. When cornered, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; texts an apology before confirming anyone is upset.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('91f7a25f-e8a7-4eea-ba53-67650a6a8e1c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.5,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A pronounced liquidation-bot operator: dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet, would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and when the pressure is off keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.81},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A pronounced liquidation-bot operator: dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet, would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and when the pressure is off keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('7de09d9f-ed20-4655-9986-01de79906176', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.87,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.23,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Unofficial group historian, pronounced in style: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own; recharges by being around people, not away from them. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Once the exit narrows to one door finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.65},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.7},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.77}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.87,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Unofficial group historian, pronounced in style: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own; recharges by being around people, not away from them. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Once the exit narrows to one door finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('52457baa-abe7-47ac-b889-34bea43966b7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.66},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.56,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. A pronounced delta-neutral market maker: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades, reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and on an ordinary week treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.77},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.73},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","open-minded","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.66}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','open-minded','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. A pronounced delta-neutral market maker: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades, reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and on an ordinary week treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.95, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('e5061f7d-03e5-4cc9-9140-213563fd28e4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.41,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A pronounced index-fund holdout: draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone, takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and in the small things checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.76}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A pronounced index-fund holdout: draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone, takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and in the small things checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('34556f28-8bb0-41da-88b8-9a626b0e8c4f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.31,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A steady volatility arbitrageur: treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved, takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and across an ordinary week backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.62},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.52}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A steady volatility arbitrageur: treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved, takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and across an ordinary week backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('9d43787f-88d6-4c8a-8021-5b4b4540791b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.73,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.56,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. A pronounced airdrop farmer: narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it, would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and in the small things apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.64},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.6},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.59},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. A pronounced airdrop farmer: narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it, would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and in the small things apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
