('c3dbbe64-e583-4f08-917a-31f81be4852c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.25,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A pronounced meme-coin rotator: narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it, reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and across an ordinary week exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.77},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.79}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A pronounced meme-coin rotator: narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it, reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and across an ordinary week exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('535fdb0f-5df4-42f4-b2b3-8074de40e8fd', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.73,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.23,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Onchain copy-trader whose defining move is that they treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. The moment it stops being hypothetical, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.73},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Onchain copy-trader whose defining move is that they treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. The moment it stops being hypothetical, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('53ff425d-ed41-4fd9-b81e-66c2173a606b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.85,"neuroticism":0.42},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.52,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.54,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Under a deadline, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. Otherwise, a pronounced group-project default leader who reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and across the quiet stretches over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.67},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.69}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","ipip-neo","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.85,"neuroticism":0.42}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','ipip-neo','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Under a deadline, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. Otherwise, a pronounced group-project default leader who reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and across the quiet stretches over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.', 0.95, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('d1695ee7-2bbf-4818-83f0-0e098a256495', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.97,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.33,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.27,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The one who remembers everyone''s order whose defining move is that they would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Once the exit narrows to one door, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; can sense a mood shift from the doorway.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.67},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.78},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.7}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","behavioral","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.97,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','behavioral','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'The one who remembers everyone''s order whose defining move is that they would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Once the exit narrows to one door, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; can sense a mood shift from the doorway.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('4358028b-dc7d-4a9c-9d5c-1cd5b07ceb39', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.62},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.24,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When there is no clean exit, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a steady penny-stock gambler who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone and notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and across the quiet stretches sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.69},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.71},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.62}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'When there is no clean exit, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a steady penny-stock gambler who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone and notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and across the quiet stretches sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('fd64b0ae-dd72-458e-bce1-949e200552fc', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.79,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.53,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.54,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The moment risk appears, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a steady event host who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely and collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and in the parts nobody grades says yes out loud and no internally.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.7},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.64}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.79,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'The moment risk appears, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a steady event host who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely and collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and in the parts nobody grades says yes out loud and no internally.', 0.91, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('d0b16f9b-29cf-4833-9682-fd5bcffea422', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.25,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. This prop-desk scalper draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone and chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. When the number turns red treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss — when the stakes are trivial, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. This prop-desk scalper draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone and chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. When the number turns red treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss — when the stakes are trivial, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('7998b9ab-c47d-4c97-bc60-8a06f90ef012', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.83,"neuroticism":0.39},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.42,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady event host who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Recharges by being around people, not away from them. When the stakes rise adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; on an ordinary week, drafts the apology before the mistake.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.71},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.64}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","temperament","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.83,"neuroticism":0.39}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','temperament','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady event host who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Recharges by being around people, not away from them. When the stakes rise adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; on an ordinary week, drafts the apology before the mistake.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
