('bcce4218-7c56-43cf-ad8d-78c7e1bdf2e7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.36,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A pronounced pairs trader: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to, defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and in the unglamorous middle of things treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.75},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.73},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.78},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A pronounced pairs trader: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to, defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and in the unglamorous middle of things treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('584f7371-2d08-4f07-837a-da66d8c5facd', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.55,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Once the exit narrows to one door, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. Otherwise, a steady discretionary swing trader who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone and absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and in the version no one reviews averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.64},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.55},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.57},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","decision-making","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','decision-making','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Once the exit narrows to one door, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. Otherwise, a steady discretionary swing trader who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone and absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and in the version no one reviews averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.94, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758b