('d363d875-d7bb-472a-8141-67f6ccc4809e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.89,"neuroticism":0.4},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.3,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Nonprofit convener whose defining move is that they reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Recharges by being around people, not away from them. When there is no clean exit, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; laughs first to test whether the room is safe to laugh.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.68},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.81},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.84}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","temperament","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.89,"neuroticism":0.4}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','temperament','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Nonprofit convener whose defining move is that they reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Recharges by being around people, not away from them. When there is no clean exit, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; laughs first to test whether the room is safe to laugh.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('27d15a83-9ff2-4f01-b691-a15c3e041925', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.83,"neuroticism":0.42},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.34,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The instant it becomes irreversible, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a steady group-project default leader who measures decisions by who they might upset and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and without an audience remembers who didn''t get invited last time.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.67},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.77},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.66}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.83,"neuroticism":0.42}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'The instant it becomes irreversible, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a steady group-project default leader who measures decisions by who they might upset and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and without an audience remembers who didn''t get invited last time.', 0.93, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('e66b327a-9c40-4425-9d25-fedb77491c43', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.41},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.35,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. A pronounced unofficial group historian: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own, reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and in the routine of it drafts the apology before the mistake.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.82},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.81}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.41}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. A pronounced unofficial group historian: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own, reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and in the routine of it drafts the apology before the mistake.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('b15f4ce8-bada-4016-924f-45f27f600e24', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.94,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.41,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Crypto day-trader, pronounced in style: narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it; defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. When the downside gets concrete takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.61},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.73},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.71},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.8}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.94,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Crypto day-trader, pronounced in style: narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it; defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. When the downside gets concrete takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('8a5a7c7b-f148-4e1a-871f-180c9c1d1a11', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.75,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.88,"neuroticism":0.35},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.51,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.36,"alpha":0.96,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. This nonprofit convener would rather lose a point than win an argument badly and recharges by being around people, not away from them. When cornered finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view — in the version no one reviews, keeps score of favors without meaning to.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.66},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.66},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.74}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","behavioral","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.75,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.88,"neuroticism":0.35}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','behavioral','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. This nonprofit convener would rather lose a point than win an argument badly and recharges by being around people, not away from them. When cornered finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view — in the version no one reviews, keeps score of favors without meaning to.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
