('edabe2f5-bbf5-4ade-aed7-682c5e271a8a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.35},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.32,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.41},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.23,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady event host who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. When there is no clean exit abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; without an audience, texts an apology before confirming anyone is upset.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.57},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.66},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.63},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.63}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","decision-making","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.35}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','decision-making','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady event host who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. When there is no clean exit abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; without an audience, texts an apology before confirming anyone is upset.', 0.91, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('ffee9b71-5e1c-4fc8-afb0-b5a7d42d8263', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.69,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.24,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the stakes rise, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. Otherwise, a steady crypto day-trader who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and measures decisions by who they might upset. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and when the pressure is off treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'When the stakes rise, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. Otherwise, a steady crypto day-trader who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and measures decisions by who they might upset. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and when the pressure is off treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('297ec115-f863-43ac-bff7-41688fb0c5fe', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.26,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady group-chat ringleader who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Once the exit narrows to one door gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; day to day, texts an apology before confirming anyone is upset.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.63},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.65}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady group-chat ringleader who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Once the exit narrows to one door gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; day to day, texts an apology before confirming anyone is upset.', 0.89, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('12fc70cb-1a26-47f8-bef9-b133ec0d6ac7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.62},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.55,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. A pronounced penny-stock gambler: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision, carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and in the parts nobody grades screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.75},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.62}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. A pronounced penny-stock gambler: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision, carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and in the parts nobody grades screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('a6822d72-9fe8-49f6-9d20-3dcf2a51fb05', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.36,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. A pronounced prop-desk scalper: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to, reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and day to day backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.78}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. A pronounced prop-desk scalper: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to, reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and day to day backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('738a8225-7b9c-4d55-9008-8d88c274de71', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.66},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.43,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. This liquidation-bot operator recharges by being around people, not away from them and gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. When the walls close in adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has — as a rule, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.68},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.66}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. This liquidation-bot operator recharges by being around people, not away from them and gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. When the walls close in adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has — as a rule, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('faa720f7-526d-4a05-9a22-91d30c5170d1', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.53,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. This the one who remembers everyone''s order takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own and chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. When cornered adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has — once the urgency drains out, laughs first to test whether the room is safe to laugh.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.66},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.71},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.63}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.84,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. This the one who remembers everyone''s order takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own and chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. When cornered adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has — once the urgency drains out, laughs first to test whether the room is safe to laugh.', 0.95, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('cd86788d-edc7-40fb-9734-4803fbf8dbb3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.47,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. A steady prop-desk scalper: dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet, reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and in the unglamorous middle of things calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. A steady prop-desk scalper: dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet, reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and in the unglamorous middle of things calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.91, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('4d56345c-07bb-4fc5-957e-9faada5b5e9a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.81,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.48,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the number turns red, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. Otherwise, a steady social-media strategist who reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it and treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and in the routine of it remembers everyone birthday and no one boundaries.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.65},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.56}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","behavioral","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.81,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','behavioral','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'When the number turns red, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. Otherwise, a steady social-media strategist who reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it and treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and in the routine of it remembers everyone birthday and no one boundaries.', 0.92, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('f2f831b5-4f38-4f2e-8656-c9b3833de6f0', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.73,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.24,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. This options seller treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved and takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. When someone is watching the outcome takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis — as a rule, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. This options seller treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved and takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. When someone is watching the outcome takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis — as a rule, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
