('1b19d351-74e0-4186-ae7c-ed5747fabc49', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.81,"neuroticism":0.42},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.43,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. A steady community manager: measures decisions by who they might upset, dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and in the version no one reviews drafts the apology before the mistake.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.62},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.64},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.77}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","temperament","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.81,"neuroticism":0.42}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','temperament','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. A steady community manager: measures decisions by who they might upset, dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and in the version no one reviews drafts the apology before the mistake.', 0.95, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('c38f5aa4-9b40-4456-b1ef-871cd8274b28', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.37},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.54,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Under pressure, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a steady team captain who measures decisions by who they might upset and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and on a slow afternoon mediates conflicts they secretly started.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.7},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.37}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Under pressure, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a steady team captain who measures decisions by who they might upset and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and on a slow afternoon mediates conflicts they secretly started.', 0.97, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
