('71a7e3e3-e683-4418-a1c6-1f41cf727db9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.69,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.85,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.27,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When someone is watching the outcome, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. Otherwise, a pronounced the friend who always drives who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault and builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and in the routine of it remembers who didn''t get invited last time.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.81},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.65},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.58}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","decision-making","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.69,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.85,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','decision-making','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'When someone is watching the outcome, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. Otherwise, a pronounced the friend who always drives who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault and builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and in the routine of it remembers who didn''t get invited last time.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('c80b26c7-779f-4a09-aefc-1cdcbb6a0fe5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.9,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.56,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.46,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Team captain, pronounced in style: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely; fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Under pressure finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.65}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","risk","ipip-neo","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.9,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','risk','ipip-neo','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Team captain, pronounced in style: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely; fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Under pressure finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('9d3c928b-81f3-4f42-88e5-5120db7a0cfb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.76,"neuroticism":0.37},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.28,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady peer mentor who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Sleeps fine the night before the big call. When the downside gets concrete takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; without an audience, remembers everyone birthday and no one boundaries.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.54},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","ipip-neo","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.76,"neuroticism":0.37}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','ipip-neo','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady peer mentor who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Sleeps fine the night before the big call. When the downside gets concrete takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; without an audience, remembers everyone birthday and no one boundaries.', 0.89, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
