('f4818645-27a3-4a02-ab2a-a9301e582c22', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.87,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.3,"narcissism":0.48,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.54,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When there is no clean exit, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a pronounced group-chat ringleader who absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and left to their own devices over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.67},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.64}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","behavioral","risk","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.87,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','behavioral','risk','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'When there is no clean exit, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a pronounced group-chat ringleader who absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and left to their own devices over-explains a boundary rather than just stating it.', 0.96, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('995d2245-8955-4273-bfe8-a4306623d083', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.81,"neuroticism":0.42},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.37,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady event host who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. In a pinch finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; in the parts nobody grades, remembers everyone birthday and no one boundaries.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.67},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.71},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.66},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.6}],"tags":["social","dependent","community","mediator","high-agreeableness","accommodating","decision-making","behavioral","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"community-peacemaker"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.81,"neuroticism":0.42}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['social','dependent','community','mediator','high-agreeableness','accommodating','decision-making','behavioral','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'A steady event host who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. In a pinch finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; in the parts nobody grades, remembers everyone birthday and no one boundaries.', 0.93, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
('382add75-e85c-4e4a-a658-d0c532ce0b76', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.69},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.26,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. This commodities speculator recharges by being around people, not away from them and reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Once things get tense jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — in the version no one reviews, exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.81},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.76},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.78}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","social-trader","fomo","outgoing","cognition","social-cascade","copy-trading","farcaster","meme-rotator"],"archetype":"rh-sentiment-follower"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.69}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','social-trader','fomo','outgoing','cognition','social-cascade','copy-trading','farcaster','meme-rotator']::text[], 'Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. This commodities speculator recharges by being around people, not away from them and reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Once things get tense jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — in the version no one reviews, exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', 'efad67da-ca57-4cd6-9238-63b66cd758bc'),
